bug.author: lutzroeder
bug.description:
Describe the current behavior TensorFlow Lite added a new operator BuiltinOptions.BATCH_MATMUL which translates to BatchMatmul but the corresponding options are named BatchMatMul. Describe the expected behavior The operator should be called BuiltinOptions.BATCH_MAT_MUL. Standalone code to reproduce the issue <denchmark-link:https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/828fe43cf3aaf1a60ed0b263d4af4b3442e79121#r38357271>828fe43#r38357271</denchmark-link>
